title: Corporate Profits Tax Liability for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As 2 Variables-- (1)--Original Data, 1939-1946 (2)--Original Data, 1946-1965. Data Reflect The Quarterly Totals At Annual Rates. Unadjusted Figures Were Multiplied By Four To Obtain Quarterly Totals At Annual Rates. Source: Department Of Commerce, National Income, 1954 Edition. A Supplement To The Survey Of Current Business, Through 1945.

This NBER data series q09074a appears on the NBER website in Chapter 9 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter09.html.
